{"id":1034,"date":"2011-09-18T03:11:14","date_gmt":"2011-09-17T23:11:14","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/www.dailyhadithonline.com\/?p=1034"},"modified":"2023-03-24T12:19:47","modified_gmt":"2023-03-24T08:19:47","slug":"spread-fasad-cut-rahim","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2011\/09\/18\/spread-fasad-cut-rahim\/","title":{"rendered":"Hadith on Rahim: Will you spread corruption, cut off your family?"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201c<strong>Verily, Allah made the creation and when He finished, the womb said: In this place, I seek refuge in you from those who sever me. Allah said: Are you not pleased that I keep good relations with those who are good to you and I will cut off whoever severs relations with you? The womb said: Yes, my Lord. Allah said: Thus, you will have it<\/strong>.\u201d Then, the Prophet said, \u201c<strong>Recite the verse if you wish: Will you then, if you were given authority, spread corruption in the land and sever your family ties<\/strong>?\u201d (47:22)<\/p>\n<p>Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 5987, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 2554<\/p>\n<p>Grade: <strong><em>Muttafaqun Alayhi<\/em><\/strong> (authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim<\/p>\n<p align=\"right\">\u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0647\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0645\u064e \u0625\u0650\u0646\u064e\u0651 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064e \u062e\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0642\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0652\u062e\u064e\u0644